overview: Legendary director Axel Braun continues his mission inside the mysteries of erotica with these exquisite ode to the most fetishized of all non-genital body parts: feet. Superstar Chanel Preston headlines a cast of beautiful women who enjoy having their toes licked, sucked, and played with, in the first volume of another Braun series destined to become a classic.
tagline: Get off on the right foot!
title: Axel Braun's Sole Mates
